<h3 id="the-stack-during-diffofsums-call">The stack during diffofsums Call</h3>

<p><img src="https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/79521972/160536148-de64e9b7-f0d9-49f6-9ec8-4249cadc2669.png" alt="image" /></p>

